Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.37,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}今日も　今日も　きっと　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.81,InsZH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}一定會有人又被你拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.81,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}誰かを救ってるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:28.87,InsZH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}最感謝的 你在我們身邊以後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:28.87,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}すんごいのは　キミの存在が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.13,InsZH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}更多 更多 永久 永久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.13,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}もっと　もっと　ずっと　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.36,InsZH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}世界的明天誕生在雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.36,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}世界の明日をつくる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:39.04,InsZH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}不要累倒了我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:39.04,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}無茶だけはしないでね…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:45.68,InsZH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}你還有我們陪伴在左右！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:45.68,InsJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)\3c&H9072FF&}ひとりじゃないんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的文化祭演出也要加油唱好哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 來喝水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,MASS竟然會誇別人 太神奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But 還不止如此哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位看過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是 RAISE A SUILEN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,縮寫就是RAS哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SUILEN？是花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.04,Tips,,0,0,0,,註：睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是日本的竹簾子 能明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是竹幕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這個名字代表的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,盛大開幕！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No！PAREO！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,RAISE A SUILEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,公布這個名字出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就代表著我們會永遠站在聚光燈下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用我最強的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,結束這個女子樂團時代！
Comment: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,EDJP P
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,New world就要開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明天開始請每天都來工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,直到首場個唱出道之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓你們達到最強的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,最強…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes 最強！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要演出多一些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那天是文化祭
